      "span_text": "The distribution of NPIs in JA JA shows two classes of NPIs: (i) NPIs that are only licensed in the domain of sentential negation, and (ii) NPIs that are licensed in the domain of DE operators. The same locality constraint applies to the restriction of the universal quantifier koll 'all'."
